LightGBM gradient boosting model for bike-sharing demand prediction.
Features: temporal (hour, weekday, month, cyclic encoding), weather,
station metadata (POI counts, location), and aggregated statistics
(station-level mean/median demand, city-level patterns).
Model trained with MAE objective, 1500 trees, early stopping.
Handles city 3 generalization via fallback to city-level aggregates.

To reproduce: cd submissions/my_team && python train.py
